# 10. Acceptance checklist

Use this checklist before integrating anywhere.

## Storage

* profile loads after refresh
* corrupted JSON does not break app
* reset works
* import/export works

## Core

* every event updates correctly
* stats clamp correctly
* stage promotion works
* mood changes make sense
* unlocks only unlock once
* history does not grow endlessly

## Anti-grind

* spamming `correct_answer` gives reduced returns
* spamming care buttons has cooldown
* very short sessions do not give full session rewards

## UI

* widget renders
* panel opens
* panel closes on outside click
* no repeated listeners after multiple opens
* actions update instantly

## Demo

* all event buttons work
* app switcher updates per-app stats
* state viewer stays in sync

