# 11. Integration contract for other apps

Every real app should only need to do three things.

## A. Load the library files

```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/shared/edupet/edupet.css">
<script src="/shared/edupet/edupet-config.js"></script>
<script src="/shared/edupet/edupet-storage.js"></script>
<script src="/shared/edupet/edupet-core.js"></script>
<script src="/shared/edupet/edupet-ui.js"></script>
```

## B. Initialise it

```js
EduPet.init({ appId: 'reading-app' });
EduPet.mount('#edupet-widget');
```

## C. Send meaningful events

```js
EduPet.recordEvent({ appId: 'reading-app', type: 'session_start' });
EduPet.recordEvent({ appId: 'reading-app', type: 'task_completed' });
EduPet.recordEvent({ appId: 'reading-app', type: 'retry_attempt' });
EduPet.recordEvent({ appId: 'reading-app', type: 'improvement_made' });
EduPet.recordEvent({ appId: 'reading-app', type: 'session_end' });
```

That is the whole contract.

